   /* magical armours */

   The black grand breastplate...
(/d/Kalad/common/central/arm/lord_breastplate.c) ... is worn
by the High Lord of Kabal, to protect him from mele attack
as well as magically attacks. It can be worn only by them
who have a dis of 70, and are almost sober. To remove it one must be almost
sober too. If they try, but fail, they will loose 50 manapoints.
AC:43
OBJ_I_RES_MAGIC : 10
OBJ_I_RES_FIRE  : 30
OBJ_I_RES_AIR   : 20
