  The holy golden platemail..
(/d/Kalad/common/raum/drakmere/arm/dl_plate) 
It is the armour worn by Lord Drakmere of the City of Drakmere
AC:44

  The robe of penthalus
(/d/Kalad/common/raum/arm/pen_robe)
 This is a magical robe of dark magic. It protects the wearer from death 
magic.
AC: 10
MAGIC_I_RES_DEATH : 50

 
  The medallion of penthalus
(/d/Kalad/common/raum/arm/pen_medallion)
  This is a very powerful and ancient medallion that has been passed down 
from master of apprentice in a long line of necromancers. It contains the 
lifes blood of a thousand sacrificed individuals. When worn, it gives the 
wearer a small fraction of their combined inttelect.
AC: 1
adds 10 int to wearer
adds 20 wis to wearer

They holy platemail of Lord Drakmere -
(/d/Kalad/common/raum/drakmere/arm/dl_plate.c)

This is a magical forged and blessed armour, resulting in higher strenght 
and durability.
AC: 44

- Ancient mithril chainmail -

This is the chainmail worn by the captain of the elite guards of the
High-Lord. He protects the lady of the High-Lord, and is very tough. See
the weapons doc on the fire axe for more info.
AC: 42/48/44

- shimmering kite-shield -
(~drakmere/arm/shim_shield)

This is from Sir Gilbert (~drakmere/npc/crystaline_knight) who, as said in
the sword entry in weapons, is hard to kill. This shield is ac 40, and
gives the wearer a +2 to light, and a magical resistance to magic +25
additive.

